Microsoft 365 Copilot and Microsoft Copilot Chat help users work faster by using artificial intelligence inside everyday productivity tools. With Microsoft 365 Copilot, you can create documents in Microsoft Word,
analyze data in Microsoft Excel, build presentations in Microsoft PowerPoint, and manage emails in Microsoft Outlook using simple prompts. Microsoft Copilot Chat provides a conversational AI experience where users can ask questions, 
generate ideas, summarize information, and get assistance across tasks. Together, these tools make it easier for individuals and teams to save time, improve productivity, and complete work more efficiently.(Priyamari)
Unlike tools that are limited to creating documents, analyzing spreadsheets, or designing presentations, Microsoft Copilot Chat functions as a standalone conversational assistant that supports a wide variety of tasks beyond any single application.(poonkundran)
Microsoft Copilot Chat enables users to interact with AI through simple conversations to ask questions, get quick answers, and generate ideas instantly, making everyday tasks easier and faster without relying on any specific application,
 Copilot helps you draft documents, create presentations, analyze data, and manage emails directly within Word, Excel, PowerPoint, and Outlook, while Chat acts like a personal assistant that can pull information from across your files, emails, and meetings to answer questions or prepare summaries. (Prabhavathi) 
Microsoft 365 Copilot & Chat is an AI-powered assistant that helps users work more efficiently within Microsoft 365 applications such as Word, Excel, PowerPoint, Outlook, and Teams. Copilot allows users to interact using natural language to generate content, summarize documents, analyze data, and automate routine tasks.
Through Copilot Chat, users can ask questions, receive suggestions, and quickly find information across their files and conversations. By integrating advanced AI capabilities with Microsoft 365 tools, Copilot enhances productivity, improves collaboration, and helps users complete tasks faster and more effectively. (Pradeep)
